**Your art prompt is a young baby with big, sparkling eyes and spiky hair that is short and clean. The baby is wearing trendy T-Rex shorts and a vibrant red baseball jacket. The baby is running at full speed, but not on the ground, they are running in deep space. As the baby runs, their best friend, a huge great white shark, is keeping pace with them. The shark has a friendly smile and is joyfully swimming through the stars, matching the baby's stride. The art style for this scene is inspired by Pixar, but with a more realistic feel. The characters have a detailed and textured design, with a sense of weight and depth that emphasizes their physical presence. The baby's big eyes have a glimmer of realistic reflection, and their spiky hair is rendered with individual strands that add to their playful character. The great white shark is impressive in its size, with realistic skin textures and details that capture the true essence of the animal. In the background of the scene are various bright and colorful stars, nebulas, and galaxies, with the Milky Way stretching across the expanse of space. The colors of the stars and galaxies are rich and vibrant, creating an otherworldly and magical atmosphere. The entire scene is filled with dynamic energy and motion, as the baby and the shark run and swim through space, seemingly weightless and free. The overall effect of the art piece is one of playful wonder and boundless imagination, but with a touch of realism that adds to the sense of awe and majesty. It's a scene that celebrates the power of imagination, and the magic of the universe, but with a sense of groundedness that makes it feel all the more real.** - <@531326782482284545> (fast)
